title: Thursday Post Show (3-11-21)
itunes:title: Thursday Post Show (3-11-21)
description:
The post show is now it’s own podcast! Bobby talks about a guy who got boo’d by an entire flight after he held them up for 90 minutes for not wearing a mask. Amy got an amazon package that was completely empty. Which of our friends would we marry? Bobby said he could marry Eddie. Amy would marry her sister.
